---
import MarketingLayout from '../../layouts/MarketingLayout.astro';
import Button from '../../components/ui/Button.astro';
---

<MarketingLayout
  title="Prijzen - Pagayo Multi-Tenant SaaS Platform"
  description="Transparante prijzen voor elk bedrijf. Start gratis, schaal op wanneer je groeit. Geen verborgen kosten."
  lang="nl"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="container mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-primary-dark mb-6">Simpele, transparante prijzen</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        Start gratis, betaal alleen voor wat je gebruikt. Upgrade of downgrade op elk moment.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing Table -->
  <section class="container mx-auto px-6 pb-20">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Free Tier -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-soft p-8 border border-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Starter</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Voor kleine projecten en testen</p>
        <div class="mb-6">
          <span class="text-4xl font-bold">€0</span>
          <span class="text-gray-600">/maand</span>
        </div>
        <Button variant="secondary" href="https://beheer.pagayo.com" class="w-full mb-8">
          Start gratis
        </Button>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary-purple mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>1 tenant</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary-purple mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Tot 100 producten</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary-purple mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>100 orders/maand</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary-purple mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Basis analytics</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary-purple mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Email support</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-gray-400 mr-2">×</span>
            <span class="text-gray-400">Custom domain</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-gray-400 mr-2">×</span>
            <span class="text-gray-400">API access</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Professional Tier (Featured) -->
      <div
        class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-strong p-8 border-2 border-primary-purple relative transform scale-105"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-primary-purple text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold"
        >
          Populair
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Professional</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Voor groeiende bedrijven</p>
        <div class="mb-6">
          <span class="text-4xl font-bold">€99</span>
          <span class="text-gray-600">/maand</span>
        </div>
        <Button variant="primary" href="https://beheer.pagayo.com" class="w-full mb-8">
          Start proefperiode
        </Button>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary-purple mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Tot 10 tenants</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary-purple mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Onbeperkt producten</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary-purple mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>5.000 orders/maand</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary-purple mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Advanced analytics</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary-purple mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Priority support</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary-purple mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Custom domains</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary-purple mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Full API access</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary-purple mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Webhooks</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Enterprise Tier -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-soft p-8 border border-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Enterprise</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Voor grote organisaties</p>
        <div class="mb-6">
          <span class="text-4xl font-bold">Custom</span>
        </div>
        <Button variant="secondary" href="/nl/contact" class="w-full mb-8"> Neem contact op </Button
        >
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary-purple mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Onbeperkt tenants</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary-purple mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Onbeperkt alles</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary-purple mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Dedicated server</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary-purple mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>24/7 phone support</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary-purple mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>SLA guarantee</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary-purple mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Custom integrations</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary-purple mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Dedicated account manager</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary-purple mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>On-premise optie</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Feature Comparison -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Volledige vergelijking</h2>
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full bg-white rounded-lg shadow-soft">
          <thead class="bg-gray-100">
            <tr>
              <th class="text-left p-4 font-bold">Feature</th>
              <th class="text-center p-4 font-bold">Starter</th>
              <th class="text-center p-4 font-bold">Professional</th>
              <th class="text-center p-4 font-bold">Enterprise</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y">
            <tr>
              <td class="p-4">Aantal tenants</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">1</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">10</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">Onbeperkt</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="p-4">Producten</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">100</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">Onbeperkt</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">Onbeperkt</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="p-4">Orders/maand</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">100</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">5.000</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">Onbeperkt</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="p-4">Custom domain</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">-</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">✓</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">✓</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="p-4">API access</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">-</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">✓</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">✓</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="p-4">Webhooks</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">-</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">✓</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">✓</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="p-4">Priority support</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">-</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">✓</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">✓</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="p-4">SLA guarantee</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">-</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">-</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">✓</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="p-4">Dedicated account manager</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">-</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">-</td>
              <td class="text-center p-4">✓</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="container mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Veelgestelde vragen</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-soft">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Kan ik op elk moment upgraden of downgraden?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Ja! Je kunt op elk moment van plan switchen. Bij upgrades betaal je direct het
            verschil pro-rata. Bij downgrades wordt het verschil verrekend met je volgende
            factuur.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-soft">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Wat gebeurt er als ik mijn limieten overschrijd?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We sturen je een notificatie als je 80% van je limiet bereikt. Bij 100% krijg je een
            upgrade suggestie, maar je service blijft gewoon actief. Overschrijdingen worden
            berekend tegen €0,10 per extra order.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-soft">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Zijn er setup kosten?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Nee, geen setup kosten. Bij Enterprise plannen helpen we gratis met onboarding en
            migratie.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-soft">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Wat is de payment processing fee?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Pagayo rekent geen extra payment fee. Je betaalt alleen de standaard Stripe/Mollie fees
            (1,9% + €0,25 voor Europese cards). Deze ga je direct met hen af.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="container mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <div
      class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-purple to-[#7A73FF] rounded-2xl p-12 text-center text-white"
    >
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Klaar om te starten?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">
        Begin vandaag met je gratis proefperiode. Upgrade wanneer je klaar bent.
      </p>
      <Button variant="secondary" href="https://beheer.pagayo.com">
        Start gratis proefperiode →
      </Button>
    </div>
  </section>
</MarketingLayout>
